    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: You get to the forest looking for revenge. You are going ot kill that guy
      for locking you up.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch seems more interested in the ones who wanted to buy the explosives.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The goblin tells her she would put her mony on them being the priests in
      the village.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch tells her that that's not possible. The priests would never
      blow up the village.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch reminds you to stack up on supplies before confronting the
      bandits. Once you find them it will be too late.
